---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="About Us — RealityCheck Tools" description="We built RealityCheck.tools to help you face the uncomfortable truth about your daily habits.">
  <div class="section-padding" style="max-width:700px;margin:0 auto;text-align:center;padding-top:48px;">
    <h1 style="font-size:48px;">About RealityCheck.tools</h1>
    <p style="color:var(--muted);font-size:16px;margin-bottom:32px;">We built this because nobody else would tell you the truth.</p>
    <div style="background:var(--surface-card);border-radius:var(--radius-lg);padding:var(--space-xl);text-align:left;">
      <p style="color:var(--body);line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:16px;font-size:15px;">Every day, we make small choices that add up to huge consequences. A coffee here, a subscription there, an hour of scrolling before bed. Individually, they feel harmless. Collectively, they shape our lives.</p>
      <p style="color:var(--body);line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:16px;font-size:15px;">RealityCheck.tools is a collection of brutally honest calculators designed to show you the real cost of your habits. No sugarcoating. No gentle nudges. Just cold, hard math served with a side of sarcasm.</p>
      <p style="color:var(--body);line-height:1.7;font-size:15px;">We believe that change starts with awareness. Sometimes you need someone (or something) to tell you the uncomfortable truth. We're that something. With 5 different tone modes, you can choose how you want to hear it — from Friendly to Indian Parent levels of guilt.</p>
    </div>
    <div style="margin-top:32px;"><a href="/" class="btn-primary">Try a Reality Check</a></div>
  </div>
</Layout>
